50 146 Td
(  - every action emits a receipt: ) Tj
50 130 Td
(  - receipts are the audit log and the truth surface) Tj
50 103 Td
(5\\\) secrets isolation \\\(required\\\)) Tj
50 87 Td
(  - write-privileged tokens live only on the executor box) Tj
